## Win/Loss Analysis

- Interview winners and losers to validate positioning and identify gaps
- Rank decision criteria from buyer interviews
- Track competitor mentions in CRM and call recordings
- Debrief sales team on evaluation process

## Common Pitfalls

- **Analysis paralysis**: Time-box research to 2-4 weeks. Decide at 70% confidence; real market feedback fills the rest.
- **Confirmation bias**: Ask open-ended questions. Interview churned customers. Seek disconfirming data.
- **Static market view**: Refresh competitive intel quarterly. Markets move faster than slide decks.
